Private Events
Celebrate your special occasions at Frenchman's Reserve Country Club.
We promise to go above and beyond to personally take care of you and your guests to ensure that you feels welcomed and beyond satisfied.
We have both indoor and outdoors spaces perfect for your event and can accommodate intimate gatherings. Whether you are planning a wedding, baby shower, meeting, birthday party, golf outing or rehearsal dinner, you will be taken care of by our experienced staff. Our goal is to make planning your event as easy as possible for you and to make you feel like a guest at your own event!
Please contact our Social Events and Catering Director,
PSaylor@Frenchmansreservecc.com
or call 561-630-0333 ext.140

Directions to Frenchman's Reserve Country Club
From Interstate 95 and Florida’s Turnpike, exit at PGA Boulevard in Palm Beach Gardens and head east. Travel in the far right lane to
the Alternate A1A ramp and head north 1 3/10 miles to the Frenchman’s Reserve entrance on the right.
Only minutes away from Frenchman’s Reserve:
I-95 (3 minute drive)
Florida Turnpike (5 minute drive)
Palm Beach International Airport (20 minute drive)
Palm Beach Gardens Medical Center (10 minute drive)
Palm Beach (15 minute drive)
Fort Lauderdale (45 minute drive)
Miami (90 minute drive)

Kids' CORE Club
The CORE (CHILL. OUT. RELAX. & EXPLORE.) Club offers complimentary childcare is provided to Members who are enjoying any of the Club’s amenities i.e. fitness, spa, golf, tennis, pool, dining or other services.  Full-day childcare is not available.  Legal and insurance requirements stipulate that the Member remain on “Club” property while children are at The CORE Club.  Kids can enjoy interacting with other children, making crafts, playing games and enjoying the Playground facility or Multi-Sports Court!

About our Golf
“Golf is deceptively simple and endlessly complicated; it satisfies the soul and frustrates the intellect. It is at the same time rewarding and maddening - and it is without a doubt the greatest game mankind has ever invented.”
An Arnold Palmer Signature Course
The championship golf course at Frenchman’s Reserve is without question the ultimate expression of the Arnold Palmer guarantee of uncompromising standards in golf course design. With large, subtle greens and fairways lined with tall Florida pines and colorful wildflowers, the course enhances the beauty of the lush South Florida landscape.
18-hole, 6,735-yard, par-72 Arnold Palmer Signature Golf Course complete with two Paspalum grass driving range tees, two practice putting greens and an expansive three green short game practice area.

Becoming a Member
At Frenchman's Reserve Country Club, benefit from resort style living, combined with family friendly warmth. We offer a spectacular environment, exciting activities, varied programming and personalized services. Frenchman's Reserve Country Club is a special place, reserved for those with a passion for life's finest. We're here to help strengthen the bonds of family, friends and community. We recognize that time together is the greatest luxury of all. At Frenchman's Reserve Country Club, we promise to provide all of the necessities for a life well lived.
Frenchman's Reserve Country Club has a membership category to fit every lifestyle.
Resident Memberships:
Full Golf Equity
